# 3️⃣ CORE PERFORMANCE DIMENSIONS

Supplier evaluation covers:

| Dimension                      | Measurement Examples                |
| ------------------------------ | ----------------------------------- |
| Timeliness                     | On-time delivery %, delay frequency |
| Quality                        | Defect rate, rework incidents       |
| Compliance                     | Adherence to contract terms         |
| Responsiveness                 | Communication speed                 |
| Financial reliability          | Payment disputes, insolvency risk   |
| Ethical conduct                | Misrepresentation, collusion flags  |
| Safety and regulatory compliance | Incident reports                    |
| Dispute history                | Arbitration or litigation cases     |

Each dimension weighted per procurement category.

