---

# 5️⃣ PERFORMANCE SCORING MODEL

---

## 🔹 A. Contract-Level Score

At completion:

```
Final Contract Performance Score =
(Timeliness × Weight)
+ (Quality × Weight)
+ (Compliance × Weight)
+ (Responsiveness × Weight)
+ (Risk Adjustments)
```

Scale example: 0–100.

---

## 🔹 B. Rolling Supplier Score

System calculates:

```
Cumulative Supplier Score =
Weighted Average of Last N Contracts
```

More recent contracts can carry higher weight.

