# 🔟 CORRECTIVE ACTION and SANCTIONS

If performance falls below threshold:

System may trigger:

* Warning notice
* Mandatory corrective action plan
* Temporary suspension
* Restricted bidding eligibility
* Full blacklisting (with approval)

All actions logged under Logic 14.

---

# 1️⃣1️⃣ DISPUTE and APPEAL FAIRNESS

Supplier can:

* View performance evaluation
* Submit rebuttal
* Provide corrective evidence
* Appeal rating decision

System must:

* Log evaluator identity
* Record justification
* Prevent anonymous rating

Ensures fairness and avoids abuse.

---

# 1️⃣2️⃣ EARLY WARNING SYSTEM

Real-time monitoring triggers alerts if:

* Delivery delay exceeds threshold
* SLA breach frequency high
* Quality defects increasing
* Communication response time deteriorates

Allows intervention before contract failure.

---

